$ Oracle: V$TYPE_SIZE
@ v$type_size

Sizes (in bytes) of some database components, to be used to estimate data block capacity.

code {
select
   component,
   type,
   description,
   type_size
from
   v$type_size
order by
   component,
   type;
code }

sa:

  This view selects from → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/instance/fixed-tables/k/q/f/sz[`x$kqfsz`].

  → development/databases/Oracle/installed/dynamic-performance-views
